818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:08:17.000Z","msg":"咩歌"},{"pid":"f26d25e47a44d9562f58740d332bdbfcdcd2d972","tid":2402852,"uid":138692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:17:11.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b204cd1a4f4ed038a459134a6e27145c038626b9","tid":2402852,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ca0ced70b66335d94a9ab2cacb8c76b118b6ed","tid":2402852,"uid":365058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab8cf343afdbf04f5fdc8177c174a8821ff0fa3","tid":2402852,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:08:17.000Z","msg":"咩歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:49:36.000Z","msg":"原來他不夠愛我？"},{"pid":"04e50cb0327ce91a4772c6e7342cd090c53b85c6","tid":2402852,"uid":310867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"全首：林鄭她封殺了我<br />\n<br />\n她不會賜予希望 <br />\n根本冇心肝<br />\n<span class=\"red\">惡毒林鄭毒婦要提防<br />\n她出薪經已斷斤磅<br />\n變食人King Kong<br />\n亦尸位民望下跌仍諉過<br />\n<br />\n明白佢愛偷漢<br />\n無懼浸豬籠入網<br />\n抽插更加爽</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭她封殺了我 堂食禁晚上入座<br />\n林鄭只愛習總龜頭 被口爆了幾多<br />\n林鄭她不會救我 從來都不懺悔過<br />\n就算確診瓜左勁多 也是我的錯<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">她黑心使我更失望 更令人不安<br />\n極刻毒涼薄毒婦 仍勾漢<br />\n<br />\n明白這個勾當 全為了中共持續作惡<br />\n吞併了香港</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭她封殺了我 堂食禁晚上入座<br />\n林鄭只愛習總龜頭 被口爆了幾多<br />\n林鄭她不會救我 從來都不懺悔過<br />\n就算確診瓜左勁多 也是我的錯<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">明白要多年持續對抗 總對她別存寄望</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭她一錯再錯 如何錯也非她的錯<br />\n林鄭她過份的黑心 每日也虧欠那麼多<br />\n林鄭她不會救我 沉迷了再三欺騙我<br />\n<span class=\"red\">惟獨我中招要被禁足 最後要一個<br />\n我無做錯</span>"},{"pid":"270ca097b036699421d8a3e0f0ed224c2a3d7f06","tid":2402852,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"本來想改呢句<br />\n<br />\n林鄭她一錯再錯 如何錯也非她的錯<br />\n<span class=\"red\">林鄭想與習總開心 要做愛抽插抽出火</span><br />\n林鄭她不會救我 沉迷了再三欺騙我<br />\n如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747a174a84fc9bf867457624b29f881a90abc10c","tid":2402852,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"一睇個名就有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae6a0e9b27ee4d215f18389414530acc4db20d7","tid":2402852,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OLX053.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OLX053.gif&h=8125854a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aeddc5e34a3eab3d3a67e7fa8782ce9f51aba89","tid":2402852,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"面癱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e691b3e298bc776d61858223bb77884ce9aa345e","tid":2402852,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be07297a30c38a586fdbfbac19d32e8810dbe6d","tid":2402852,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a